  "title": "ISic001526. I.Sicily inscription 001526",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυρακὴ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυρακὴ\"><span data-text=\"Κυρακὴ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Κυρακή\">Κυρακὴ</span></span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ἐνθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"κεῖ\n                    τε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κεῖ-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>τε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζησε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">η͡σ</span>ε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡η</span></span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"β𐅵\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"β𐅵\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">β</span>𐅵</span>´ <span data-text=\"ἐτάφη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"τάπτω\">ἐτάφη</span>  <span data-text=\"τες\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\"><span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡ε</span>ς</span>  <span data-text=\"κ\" data-n=\"42\" data-lemma=\"κ\">κ</span>´ <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">τοῦ</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὀκτωβρίου\"><span data-text=\"Ὀκτωβρίου\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"October\">Ὀκτωβ(ρίου)</span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Κυρακὴ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Κυρακή\">Κυρακὴ</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ἐνθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"κεῖτε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κεῖτε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζησε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"β𐅵\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"β𐅵\">β𐅵</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐτάφη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"τάπτω\">ἐτάφη</span>  <span data-text=\"τες\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">τες</span>  <span data-text=\"κ\" data-n=\"42\" data-lemma=\"κ\">κ</span>  <span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">τοῦ</span>  <span data-text=\"Ὀκτωβρίου\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"October\">Ὀκτωβρίου</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυρακὴ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυρακὴ\"><span data-text=\"Κυρακὴ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Κυρακή\">ΚΥΡΑΚΗ</span></span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κεῖ\n                    τε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΕΙ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Η͡Σ</span>Ε</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">Ε<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"β𐅵\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"β𐅵\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Β</span>𐅵</span><span data-text=\"ἐτάφη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"τάπτω\">ΕΤΑΦΗ</span><span data-text=\"τες\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\"><span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Ε</span>Σ</span><span data-text=\"κ\" data-n=\"42\" data-lemma=\"κ\">Κ</span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΟΥ</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὀκτωβρίου\"><span data-text=\"Ὀκτωβρίου\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"October\">ΟΚΤΩΒ</span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Κυρακὴ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Κυρακή\">ΚΥΡΑΚΗ</span><span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κεῖτε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΕΙΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"β𐅵\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"β𐅵\">Β𐅵</span><span data-text=\"ἐτάφη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"τάπτω\">ΕΤΑΦΗ</span><span data-text=\"τες\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΕΣ</span><span data-text=\"κ\" data-n=\"42\" data-lemma=\"κ\">Κ</span><span data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"Ὀκτωβρίου\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"October\">ΟΚΤΩΒΡΙΟΥ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after Curbera 1995</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Curbera convincingly suggests that the second character on line 4 is the Greek symbol for one half, found in papyri and inscriptions, giving an age of 2.5, rather than an inverted numeral 32 or 12 with a Latin L or a Greek iota.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 45.1417 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Orsi 1896 54 no. 88 (357) <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001710\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001710</a>  </li><li> Agnello 1953 no.30 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002211\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002211</a>  </li><li> Ferrua 1989 no.148 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995</a>  </li><li> Curbera 1995 100 no.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001489\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001489</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
